duties_responsibilities.duty: Provide high-quality patient care in various healthcare settings, including general, ortho, urology, hearts, heads, trauma, neuro, and pediatrics, as well as obstetric cases.
Work collaboratively with MDs and other healthcare professionals with a flexible and adaptable approach.
Choose assignments that offer a balanced work-life schedule and engaging patient interactions.

education_certification.credential: Diploma in Anesthesiology or related medical field (Board Certification preferred)
